#
# @title Check iNode Usage
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# @author Myles McNamara
# @date 12/18/2012
# @version 1.0
# @source http://github.com/tripflex
# @description Check the amount of inodes (files) in a given directory.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# @usage ./checkinodeusage <path>
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
